                    <div class="bg-neutral p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 font-serif text-primary"><i class="fas fa-bible mr-2"></i> The Holy Scriptures</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">We believe the Bible, consisting of the Old and New Testaments, is the inspired, infallible, and authoritative Word of God. It is the supreme and final authority in all matters of faith and conduct, guiding our lives and doctrines.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-neutral p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 font-serif text-primary"><i class="fas fa-cross mr-2"></i> The One True God</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">We believe in one God, eternally existent in three persons: Father, Son (Jesus Christ), and Holy Spirit. He is the Creator of all things, infinitely perfect, and worthy of all worship and praise.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-neutral p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 font-serif text-primary"><i class="fas fa-church mr-2"></i> Salvation Through Christ</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">We believe that salvation is a gift from God, received through grace by faith in Jesus Christ alone. His atoning sacrifice on the cross provides forgiveness of sins and eternal life for all who believe.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-neutral p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 font-serif text-primary"><i class="fas fa-dove mr-2"></i> The Holy Spirit</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">We believe in the present ministry of the Holy Spirit, by whose indwelling the Christian is enabled to live a godly life, and by whose power the church is empowered to carry out Christ's mission.</p>
